<div class="page-about section-padding">
  <div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
    <header class="page-about__header text-center">
      <h1 class="page-about__title">{{ page.title }}</h1>
      <p class="page-about__subtitle">Luxury botanical skincare inspired by Ayurvedic traditions and modern science.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="page-about__content">
      
      <section class="page-about__block">
        <h2 class="page-about__heading">Our Story</h2>
        <p>Born from a deep reverence for the natural world, CHIC was founded with a singular vision: to bridge the ancient wisdom of Ayurvedic healing with state-of-the-art dermatological science. What began as a passionate exploration of potent plant extracts has evolved into a comprehensive collection of luxury skincare rituals. We believe that true beauty stems from balance, and every product we craft is a testament to the harmonizing power of nature.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-about__block">
        <h2 class="page-about__heading">Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>At the core of CHIC is the philosophy that skincare is not merely a routine, but a sacred ritual. We celebrate the sensory experience of skincare—the rich textures, the grounding botanical aromas, and the visible vitality it brings to the skin. Our approach is holistic; we treat the skin as an ecosystem that thrives when nourished with uncompromised, living ingredients.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-about__block">
        <h2 class="page-about__heading">Botanical Ingredients</h2>
        <p>We source our ingredients with uncompromising rigor. From wild-harvested Neem and Calendula to cold-pressed seed oils, every botanical active is selected for its clinical efficacy and purity. We refuse to use synthetic fillers, ensuring that every drop in our amber glass bottles serves a purpose. Nature provides the complex molecular structures; we simply harvest them at their peak.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-about__block">
        <h2 class="page-about__heading">Our Promise</h2>
        <p>We promise transparency, sustainability, and efficacy. Our formulations are cruelty-free, meticulously tested for safety, and packaged with a deep respect for the environment. When you choose CHIC, you are not just caring for your skin—you are investing in a mindful, luxurious practice that honors both you and the earth.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .page-about {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .page-about__header {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }
  .page-about__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    color: #2F342C; /* Dark Olive */
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .page-about__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #5F715A; /* Botanical Green */
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .page-about__block {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .page-about__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    color: #2F342C;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-about__heading::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: #5F715A;
  }
  .page-about__content p {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(47, 52, 44, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-about {
      padding: 5rem 0;
    }
    .page-about__header {
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .page-about__block {
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>

